  # 3D Hero Section Template in Framer
  
  This is a 3D hero section template in [Framer](https://framer.university/free-account) that helps you explore responsive structure, code components, video integration, element animations, and reusable components. Remix the file to dig into how the entire template is built and how the pieces work together.
  
